data.description: MOTIVATED! Seller to credit buyers with $3,000 toward buyers closing expenses or toward rate buy down with acceptable offer. Nestled in the tranquil Hiara Heights neighborhood, this split foyer gem is ready to welcome you with open arms. With 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and a host of recent updates, this property offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience.   It is conveniently located near schools, shopping, parks, Eastman and Domtar. The current owners have installed new flooring, light fixtures, a privacy fence, and water heater. Do not miss out on this one!
